00:05:35.502 --> 00:06:20.920
I asked the Lord if they were actually going to hire people to do this, and the Lord said, 'No, this is a satanic agenda that's going to come against people's minds that already have a weakness of mental disturbance.

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:44.000
' He told me this was an assignment from principalities and they were going to come against the Second Amendment.

