The Lord said this is how they're going to run their campaign in 2024, and He said you need to tell the people to pray and hear the voice of the Lord concerning every place they go in their day-to-day activity: major events, crowds, and concerts.

00:07:45.599 --> 00:08:08.759
That's why I prayed for protection for Coachella this year; the Lord had me praying against violent acts of terrorism.

00:08:09.039 --> 00:08:26.135
I know they're heathen people, probably acting crazy, but we don't need terrorism in any shape or form.

00:08:26.135 --> 00:08:27.314
Ever.

00:08:27.314 --> 00:08:47.547
We are the salt of the earth, and we pray for people's protection at all costs.

00:08:51.945 --> 00:08:57.514
We pray for them to find Jesus and have a relationship with the Lord.

00:08:57.514 --> 00:09:12.327
We don't need them going home before we reach them.

00:09:12.327 --> 00:09:22.250
We pray for all hidden things to be revealed.

00:09:22.250 --> 00:09:58.569
If there are plots and plans by lone wolf idiots like this guy in Maine, we pray the Holy Spirit would show us things to come and that angels would protect the people.

00:10:01.013 --> 00:10:22.433
If the Lord warns you about going to a place and says, 'Do not go there today,' listen to His voice.

00:10:22.433 --> 00:10:27.366
He's trying to protect you.

00:10:27.366 --> 00:10:39.373
Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 are what we stand by.

00:10:39.373 --> 00:10:52.513
We have a covenant with a God who is a protector.

00:10:56.292 --> 00:11:19.687
A thousand shall fall at our side and ten thousand at our right hand, but it will not come nigh us.

00:11:22.453 --> 00:11:42.489
The name of the Lord is a strong tower, and the righteous run into it and they are safe.

00:11:42.489 --> 00:11:59.857
I believe He is our divine protection, but we have to listen to Him.

00:11:59.857 --> 00:12:13.949
Every morning say, 'Father, I thank you that you're leading and guiding me today.

00:12:13.949 --> 00:12:25.640
Show me where I'm supposed to be.

00:12:25.640 --> 00:12:48.829
If I'm not supposed to go to the bowling alley or to Walmart today, show me.

00:12:48.829 --> 00:13:08.747
' Humble yourself under the mighty hand of God because He will protect you.

00:13:21.880 --> 00:13:25.279
He will send His angels to keep charge over you.

00:13:30.087 --> 00:13:39.160
I warned you this was coming, and it will become more frequent.

00:13:40.906 --> 00:14:20.363
The Lord said to be watchful because the devil knows his time is short and is trying to get as many people as he can to go to hell, which was never designed for you.

00:14:31.246 --> 00:14:31.623
The Lord warned me about the oil.

00:14:41.610 --> 00:15:06.827
A day or two ago, an article in Forbes magazine said they believe oil could go to $200 a barrel because of the war in the Middle East with Israel.

00:15:06.827 --> 00:15:14.342
This is another thing I prophesied.

00:15:14.342 --> 00:15:37.083
The Lord told me we would have an acceleration in the war, signs in the heavens, and the economy.

00:15:37.083 --> 00:16:06.920
I gave you the word about crypto, and two days later Bitcoin went up to 35,000 or 36,000 after being dormant for months.

00:16:06.920 --> 00:16:13.120
These are signs.

00:16:13.120 --> 00:16:30.920
A lot of people were upset about Pastor Steve's ten-year window.

00:16:42.652 --> 00:16:42.999
We occupy until He comes.

00:16:42.999 --> 00:17:26.804
Pastor Steve is a brilliant man; while some didn't like the ten-year timeline, I want everyone to come on and have an opinion.

00:17:34.876 --> 00:17:43.360
We don't need sugar-coated words; we need words that challenge us to grow.

00:17:43.360 --> 00:17:55.945
If we have ten years, we will go through more birthing pains.

00:17:55.945 --> 00:18:25.663
Everything the Lord showed me, from the 350 million people going home to the supernatural wealth transfer through crypto, gold, and silver, is coming.

00:18:26.786 --> 00:18:41.173
