00:18:41.173 --> 00:19:01.040
God will bring you witty ideas and creative ideas to get wealth.

00:19:01.040 --> 00:19:06.840
This is an acceleration of finances.

00:19:06.840 --> 00:19:16.060
God is not in a hurry.

00:19:16.060 --> 00:19:32.227
Ten years is nothing compared to the last thousands of years.

00:19:36.549 --> 00:19:51.826
It took many prophets decreeing a Savior is coming for the manifestation of Jesus to happen the first time.

00:20:04.428 --> 00:20:04.771
Now, the prophetic voices are decreeing that Jesus is coming again.

00:20:04.771 --> 00:20:13.520
He's speaking to me, 'Tell them I'm coming, Brandon.

00:20:13.520 --> 00:20:29.460
' For the last 2,000 years, we've been proclaiming Jesus is coming.

00:20:30.915 --> 00:20:49.900
I personally believe we have at least six years because we missed the shmita cycle.

00:20:49.900 --> 00:21:23.480
According to Rabbi Jonathan Cahn's book, every shmita cycle is an opportunity for decreeing Rosh Hashanah Hashanah for the rapture to take place.

00:21:23.480 --> 00:21:40.950
I believe we have six years left until the next shmita cycle.

00:21:40.950 --> 00:21:58.780
That cycle opens a seven-year window for the tribulation before the thousand-year reign.

00:22:04.380 --> 00:22:29.216
