00:22:29.216 --> 00:22:34.178
That's my personal opinion.

00:22:34.178 --> 00:22:45.320
Don't get hung up on it; instead, pray and fast.

00:22:45.320 --> 00:23:12.977
We have an escapism mentality, but the armor of the body of Christ was designed to march forward, never to retreat.

00:23:12.977 --> 00:23:20.208
