00:23:24.600 --> 00:23:41.413
The Lord told me He never designed our armor for retreat, but to take dominion and authority.

00:23:41.413 --> 00:24:11.590
Look at the helmet of salvation, the breastplate of righteousness, the belt of truth, the shield of faith, and the sword of the spirit.

00:24:11.590 --> 00:24:22.980
