00:24:22.980 --> 00:24:38.937
Tell them there's a hell to shun and a heaven to gain.

00:24:49.950 --> 00:24:50.159
We shouldn't be in retreat mode or hiding.

00:24:50.159 --> 00:25:09.862
We need to get the gospel out, lay hands on the sick, and cast out devils.

00:25:09.862 --> 00:25:16.375
We've got to win the lost.

00:25:16.885 --> 00:25:32.223
The spiritual attack has been crazy, but I'm not scared of the devil.

00:25:32.223 --> 00:25:38.474
No weapon formed against me shall prosper.

00:25:38.474 --> 00:25:56.679
